            <div class="title">
                Coal (Increased Output)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/436297ef-ba7e-48eb-9216-804637681dcc/RailwayFreightsAndFares" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
