            <div class="col-xs-12">
                <div class="actions">
                    <div class="share-debate">
                        <a href="#debate-3098727" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this debate" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div> Share
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


</div>


    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>21 March 1951</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 485</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">
<div class="content-item" id="contribution-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637">
                Mr. Murray
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">(<em>by Private Notice</em>) asked the Minister of Fuel and Power whether he has any statement to make in regard to the prospects for coal supplies to industry during the remaining winter months.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-43136771-69e2-4132-a749-d2092d36a637">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca">
                The Minister of Fuel and Power (Mr. Philip Noel-Baker)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The House may recall that in a debate on 1st February, I said that, in view of the greatly increased consumption of coal and the necessity to <span id="2424" class="column-number" data-column-number="2424"></span> build up power station stocks, I had informed the Federation of British Industries, the Trades Union Congress and Chairmen of the Regional Boards for Industry in the Emergency Committee of the National Production Advisory Council for Industry that it might not be possible during the winter months, to deliver to industrial firms more than 85 per cent., on the average, of the coal which I had planned that they should have. I expressed the hope, which I had previously expressed to the Emergency Committee, that industry would help the nation and themselves by exercising every reasonable economy in their use of coal. To that invitation, industry in general made a very handsome response, for which I should like to thank all concerned.<p></p> Fortunately, in addition to the economies in consumption which were made, the output of coal from the mines also substantially improved. Thanks to these better supplies, it has proved possible to deliver to industry, not 85 per cent., but, on the average, 95 per cent. of their programmed requirements. I think it is now possible to say that we shall maintain a high rate of delivery during the remaining weeks before the winter period ends; that is to the end of April.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-41b2aec7-28bf-4b52-b1ce-47f63fff72ca">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The end of April?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-c8ac715f-d4b9-4519-97f1-4f3f0eb2e07b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001">
                Mr. Noel-Baker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Yes, the end of April. The coal year is divided into a winter period and a summer period, each of six months. I have also every hope that industrial stocks will, at the end of April, be as high as we had originally planned, namely, three weeks consumption.<p></p> I think it is desirable that the directors and managers of industrial firms should know how considerably the situation has improved. But I add that it remains of the highest importance, not only for this year, but for the future, that industry should make the most efficient possible use of the coal which they receive, and that modern methods and equipment to this end should be generally and speedily introduced.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-21/debates/e720b87e-b8e6-450c-8cbc-faa800797b62/Coal(IncreasedOutput)#contribution-94b70167-1c35-4cb0-8898-dc60fb43c001">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-32be316f-7476-4cf9-b90c-deb3a18e47d7">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-32be316f-7476-4cf9-b90c-deb3a18e47d7">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
